channel.title: Leap - Pieter van Boven [House]
channel.description:
From all the concepts I made this year, I struggled the most with this track. I wanted it to be a more ambient track, but then I realised this was a perfect opportunity for some house.
It has some snappy beats and bongos. Enjoy!
Link: https://soundcloud.com/ietervanoven/leap
